## 15. What is Mongoose?
Mongoose is an ODM (Object Data Modeling) library for MongoDB.

Schema Example:
```js
const mongoose = require("mongoose");

const userSchema = new mongoose.Schema({
   name:String,
   age:Number
});

module.exports =
mongoose.model("User", userSchema);

